# `useTl` — text animations

Reveal, hide and switch text. Powered by GSAP's **TextPlugin** (typewriter) and
**SplitText** (per-char/word/line stagger).

```ts
tl.step().textTypeIn(".headline")                  // typewriter in
  .step().textSplitIn(".tagline", { by: "words" }) // chars | words | lines
  .step().textSwap(".headline", "New text!")   // retype to a new string
  .step()
```

